  - Format: PDF (non-password-protected; printable; PDF/A acceptable)
  - Languages: Greek and/or English
  - Issuer: Accredited Certification Body (CB) participating in the IAF MLA (e.g., accredited by ESYD or another IAF signatory Accreditation Body)
