  - Certificate Identification:
      • Certificate Number (unique)
      • Issue Date / Expiry Date
      • Original Certification Date
      • Recertification Cycle (3-year cycle), Surveillance Frequency (annual)
  - Scope Statement:
      • Covers PKI/CA operations, RA operations, HSM lifecycle, issuance/revocation/status services (CRL/OCSP), and supporting infrastructure/security operations relevant to Qualified Trust Services
  - Sites and Multi-site Scheme (if applicable):
      • List all covered sites/locations/colocations; indicate multi-site sampling model if used
  - Attachments:
      • Certificate Schedule and (if provided) Covered Sites Annex
      • Reference to the Statement of Applicability (SoA) (kept internally, but ideally referenced)
  - Validation:
      • Public verification link or QR code to CB directory (recommended)
      • Accreditation details of the CB (AB name, accreditation ID)

